{"tid":678673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「埃及文明」冒起　BBC瀕拆檔","createTime":"2018-05-26T09:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T20:44:20.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"50a77e070ec2938fcd3594882d78fb3623bd83a1","tid":678673,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"利物浦前線三叉戟穆罕默德沙拿、羅拔圖法明奴及沙迪奧文尼組成的「埃及文明」今季強勢崛起，打破多項球會乃至歐洲賽的入球紀錄，氣勢完全力壓歐聯決賽對手皇家馬德里瀕臨拆檔、由基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）、加里夫巴利及賓施馬的「BBC」組合。<br />\n歐聯四強激戰過後，利物浦已破紀錄在歐聯攻入46球，「埃及文明」中沙拿和法明奴皆入11球，文尼亦有九球進賬，合計31球已超越皇馬「BBC」2013/14球季創下的28球紀錄，成為歐聯史上入球量最高的「三叉戟」，三人當然也成為歐洲炙手可熱的攻擊組合。<br />\n而且，英超煞科戰紅軍主場4:0炒白禮頓時，沙拿仍與熱刺前鋒哈利卡尼競爭英超金靴獎，因此文尼單刀也願意橫傳予位置不算很理想的沙拿，雖然最後未能射入，不過亦可見三人之間沒有「爭食」的情況發生，「埃及文明」面對歐聯場均1.2個失球的皇馬，隨時再刷新入球紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反觀曾經殺聲震天的「BBC」，由於加里夫巴利常受傷患困擾，賓施馬狀態下滑，今季要到西甲第20輪賽事才一起上陣，其中巴利的地位深受艾斯高、馬高阿辛斯奧、盧卡斯華斯基斯等後起之秀挑戰，甚至有傳今夏或離隊。"},{"pid":"5233b0579380c14567bcfeec67feccceb28351f0","tid":678673,"uid":17081,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://en.afriquesports.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/05/Le-trio-Man%C3%A9-Salah-Firmino-dattaque-contre-Manchester-City.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.afriquesports.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2018%2F05%2FLe-trio-Man%25C3%25A9-Salah-Firmino-dattaque-contre-Manchester-City.png&h=b4c9973b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dAJZE7Tp-OI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FdAJZE7Tp-OI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d3b04f83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10bf9006af4187a51278509338f559d4db5d5927","tid":678673,"uid":80183,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5233b0579380c14567bcfeec67feccceb28351f0","tid":678673,"uid":17081,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://en.afriquesports.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/05/Le-trio-Man%C3%A9-Salah-Firmino-dattaque-contre-Manchester-City.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.afriquesports.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2018%2F05%2FLe-trio-Man%25C3%25A9-Salah-Firmino-dattaque-contre-Manchester-City.png&h=b4c9973b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dAJZE7Tp-OI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FdAJZE7Tp-OI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d3b04f83&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"想俾文尼大大力禁住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f393c79cad554882a5a5c6cab0c43773ee8f57","tid":678673,"uid":17628,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"廢綿龍拎住個波，BBC點踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5c83aec59391b2c14f518076d73c04445da833","tid":678673,"uid":90767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"等左呢晚好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9eccf6c2afefc7fa3fcfea5db4eb3fb15f7a38","tid":678673,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73be630e1d0ff84ae1102682343ac43411df71b5","tid":678673,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"皇馬出442"},{"pid":"05e00f0e6fe0049f39e4019a79dce9a1358c2d4d","tid":678673,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9df5d250a3f6e9b6b6071f67f2b5bc3a46fba94a","tid":6